body:
Pending Job Posting - Action May Be Required


        .ReadMsgBody {width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;}
        .ExternalClass {width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff;}
        body     {width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; margin:0; padding:0; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;}
        table {border-collapse: collapse;}
        .bti-email-button {
			background: #57C4E2;
			padding: 12px 18px 12px 18px; 
			margin: 0  auto;
        }

		@media only screen and (max-width: 800px)  {

	        .bti-email-container {
				width: 100%;
				background: #57C4E2;
				text-align: center;
	        }
	        .bti-email-button {
	        	text-align: center;
	        }

		}

        .bti-email-button-link {
			font-size: 16px; 
			font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
			text-align: center;
			font-weight: normal; color: #ffffff; 
			text-decoration: none; 
			display: inline-block;
        }
		@media only screen and (max-width: 800px)  {
		    body[yahoo] .deviceWidth {width:90%!important; padding:0;}
		    body[yahoo] .center {text-align: left!important;}
		    body[yahoo] .footer {text-align: center!important;}

		}

































	                        Pending Job Posting














						Stephanie,







						Thank you for using the Health Center Careers. 







						Your recent job posting, Doro Guide - Social Worker, is currently in a pending status awaiting activation. 







						To complete the posting process, please sign in to your account.















                Manage Jobs



















							Please do not reply to this email.  We are unable to respond to inquiries sent to this address. 


								If you need assistance, you can access the Help link on the top right of any career center page 
								immediately under the navigation.

